            "title": "The Microphones – &quot;The Glow&quot; Pt. 2",
            "summary": "偶然一次，在图书馆复习完后，打开b站，想搜搜有什么好听的音乐，神奇的大数据给我推了这个音乐专辑。感觉很独特，如同徒步在田野，又像在攀登高山，平静的诉说，又忽然暴起。每一次呐喊好像诉说着生命的无意，又在不断寻找新生，今天就让我们来欣赏这首音乐专辑，一定要连起来听！ 专辑详情：The Microphones – \"The Glow\" Pt. 2 – CD&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>        偶然一次，在图书馆复习完后，打开b站，想搜搜有什么好听的音乐，神奇的大数据给我推了这个音乐专辑。感觉很独特，如同徒步在田野，又像在攀登高山，平静的诉说，又忽然暴起。每一次呐喊好像诉说着生命的无意，又在不断寻找新生，今天就让我们来欣赏这首音乐专辑，一定要连起来听！</p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"270\" height=\"241\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/responsive/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2-xs.jpg 640w ,https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/responsive/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2-sm.jpg 768w ,https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/responsive/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2-md.jpg 1024w ,https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/responsive/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/responsive/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://ripponyun.github.io/media/posts/4/responsive/R-495810-1598558221-4432-2-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></figure>\n<p>专辑详情：<a href=\"https://www.discogs.com/release/495810-The-Microphones-The-Glow-Pt-2\">The Microphones – \"The Glow\" Pt. 2 – CD (Album), 2001 [r495810] | Discogs</a></p>\n<p> 音乐风格：Lo-fi、独立民谣、环境音乐、噪音摇滚、前卫民谣</p>\n<div class=\"\">\n<p>专辑曲目  ：</p>\n<div class=\"track-list\">\n<ul class=\"track-items indent\">\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"1.\">I Want Wind To Blow 5:32</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"2.\">The Glow Pt. 2 4:58</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"3.\">The Moon 5:17</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"4.\">Headless Horseman 3:10</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"5.\">My Roots Are Strong And Deep 1:53</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"6.\">Instrumental 1:38</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"7.\">The Mansion 3:34</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"8.\">Untitled 1:43</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"9.\">(Something) 2:53</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"10.\">I'll Not Contain You 2:50</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"11.\">The Gleam Pt. 2 1:58</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"12.\">Map 5:01</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"13.\">You'll Be In The Air 2:41</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"14.\">I Want To Be Cold 1:41</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"15.\">I Am Bored 1:36</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"16.\">I Felt My Size 2:19</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"17.\">Instrumental 1:56</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"18.\">I Felt Your Shape 1:55</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"19.\">Samurai Sword 4:07</li>\n<li class=\"indent\" data-track-order=\"20.\">My Warm Blood 9:29</li>\n</ul>\n<p>欣赏地址：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1V4421f7JL/?spm_id_from=333.1387.favlist.content.click&amp;vd_source=58dbac923f1ecc9fe31b69c945df0709\">【HiRes无损】The Microphones2001《The Glow, Pt. 2》每天音乐专辑分享，站内最高音质，进来听听看_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></p>\n<p class=\"video-title special-text-indent\" title=\"【全专精翻+深度解析】独立民谣最动人的秋之篇章，微光消散后的个人感情沉溺与深刻自然思索 [The Microphones - The Glow Pt. 2]\" data-title=\"【全专精翻+深度解析】独立民谣最动人的秋之篇章，微光消散后的个人感情沉溺与深刻自然思索 [The Microphones - The Glow Pt. 2]\">全专精翻+深度解析：推荐这位up</p>\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV15u47zsE8D/?spm_id_from=333.1387.favlist.content.click&amp;vd_source=58dbac923f1ecc9fe31b69c945df0709\">【全专精翻+深度解析】独立民谣最动人的秋之篇章，微光消散后的个人感情沉溺与深刻自然思索 [The Microphones - The Glow Pt. 2]_哔哩哔哩_bilibili</a></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>希望能够一个人走路时，慢慢的，静静的欣赏。</div>\n</div>",
